A: I'm not sure what you mean by "at a single time".  If you want to split the string into 3 parts, you can do this:
String[] parts = number.split("[()]");

If you want to split the string into 3 parts, but you want to keep the parentheses, you can do this:
String[] parts = number.split("(\\()|(\\))");
